headline: Hookipa Pharma announces workforce reduction of 80%, pause of eseba-vec program
summary: In a regulatory filing on Wednesday, Hookipa Pharma (HOOK) announced that on November 18, the company approved a plan to continue to improve its cost structure and operating efficiency, which includes a reduction in the company’s workforce by approximately 80% of the company’s then-current employee base.
